 font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003ctime datetime\u003d\"2025-10-24T04:56:00.000Z\"\u003e24/10/2025\u003c/time\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/tin-lien-quan-t41435123.epi\" class\u003d\"related inline !text-[#adb5bd] hover:!text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e2\n   \u003c!-- --\u003e li\u0026ecirc;n quan\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/han-quoc-lai-to-binh-si-trieu-tien-xam-pham-ranh-gioi-quan-su-r53572328.epi\" class\u003d\"origin item-origin\" target\u003d\"_blank\" rel\u003d\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGốc\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003ch3 class\u003d\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\"\u003eH\u0026agrave;n Quốc h\u0026ocirc;m nay (24/10) cho biết binh l\u0026iacute;nh CHDCND Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n lại tiếp tục c\u0026oacute; h\u0026agrave;nh vi vượt qua ranh giới qu\u0026acirc;n sự li\u0026ecirc;n Triều (MDL).\u003c/h3\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [\u0026amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;div]:mb-[15px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eQu\u0026acirc;n đội \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/han-quoc-tag2475.epi\"\u003eH\u0026agrave;n Quốc\u003c/a\u003e cho biết, h\u0026ocirc;m 19/10 vừa qua, một nh\u0026oacute;m khoảng 20 binh sĩ của Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n đ\u0026atilde; vượt qua ranh giới qu\u0026acirc;n sự li\u0026ecirc;n Triều (MDL) ở khu vực ph\u0026iacute;a Nam, thuộc tỉnh Gyeonggi. Sau khi ph\u0026aacute;t hiện vụ việc, lực lượng bảo vệ bi\u0026ecirc;n giới H\u0026agrave;n Quốc đ\u0026atilde; d\u0026ugrave;ng loa ph\u0026oacute;ng thanh để cảnh b\u0026aacute;o, nhưng nh\u0026oacute;m binh sĩ n\u0026ecirc;u tr\u0026ecirc;n vẫn tiếp tục đi s\u0026acirc;u hơn về ph\u0026iacute;a H\u0026agrave;n Quốc, khiến ph\u0026iacute;a H\u0026agrave;n Quốc phải nổ s\u0026uacute;ng cảnh c\u0026aacute;o.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url(\u0027https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:390px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"Trạm g\u0026aacute;c qu\u0026acirc;n đội H\u0026agrave;n Quốc tại khu vực phi qu\u0026acirc;n sự li\u0026ecirc;n Triều. Ảnh: Yonhap.\" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"390\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eTrạm g\u0026aacute;c qu\u0026acirc;n đội H\u0026agrave;n Quốc tại khu vực phi qu\u0026acirc;n sự li\u0026ecirc;n Triều. Ảnh: Yonhap.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eQu\u0026acirc;n đội H\u0026agrave;n Quốc cũng khẳng định, sau khi nổ s\u0026uacute;ng cảnh c\u0026aacute;o, nh\u0026oacute;m binh sĩ \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/trieu-tien-tag552.epi\"\u003eTriều Ti\u0026ecirc;n\u003c/a\u003e kh\u0026ocirc;ng c\u0026oacute; phản ứng bất thường v\u0026agrave; đ\u0026atilde; rời khỏi l\u0026atilde;nh thổ H\u0026agrave;n Quốc.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eHiện nay ph\u0026iacute;a Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n vẫn chưa l\u0026ecirc;n tiếng ch\u0026iacute;nh thức về vấn đề n\u0026agrave;y. Tuy nhi\u0026ecirc;n, theo giới quan s\u0026aacute;t, động th\u0026aacute;i n\u0026agrave;y c\u0026oacute; khả năng l\u0026agrave;m quan hệ hai miền Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n tiếp tục trở n\u0026ecirc;n phức tạp, khi H\u0026agrave;n Quốc nhiều lần c\u0026aacute;o buộc Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n c\u0026oacute; những h\u0026agrave;nh vi tương tự. Trước đ\u0026oacute;, Bộ Tư lệnh Li\u0026ecirc;n Hợp Quốc tại H\u0026agrave;n Quốc (UNC) x\u0026aacute;c nhận việc khoảng 30 binh sĩ của CHDCND Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n đ\u0026atilde; vượt qua ranh giới \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/the-gioi.epi\"\u003equ\u0026acirc;n sự\u003c/a\u003e li\u0026ecirc;n Triều v\u0026agrave;o h\u0026ocirc;m 19/8.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTiếp đ\u0026oacute;, Bộ Tổng tham mưu li\u0026ecirc;n qu\u0026acirc;n H\u0026agrave;n Quốc cho biết, h\u0026ocirc;m 26/9, một t\u0026agrave;u mang hạm tịch CHDCND Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n đ\u0026atilde; vượt qua đường ph\u0026acirc;n định ranh giới tr\u0026ecirc;n biển giữa hai miền Triều Ti\u0026ecirc;n ở Ho\u0026agrave;ng Hải, hay c\u0026ograve;n gọi l\u0026agrave; đường giới hạn ph\u0026iacute;a Bắc (NLL). Lực lượng thực thi \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/phap-luat.epi\"\u003eph\u0026aacute;p luật\u003c/a\u003e tr\u0026ecirc;n biển của H\u0026agrave;n Quốc cũng đ\u0026atilde; phải nổ s\u0026uacute;ng cảnh c\u0026aacute;o. Sau đ\u0026oacute;, t\u0026agrave;u n\u0026agrave;y đ\u0026atilde; rời khỏi hải phận H\u0026agrave;n Quốc.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text body-author text-right\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTuấn Nhật/VOV-Tokyo\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp\" tabindex\u003d\"-1\" role\u003d\"dialog\" aria-hidden\u003d\"true\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__bg\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__scroll-wrap\"\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__container\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__top-bar\"\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__counter\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title\u003d\"Close (Esc)\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--share\" title\u003d\"Share\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--fs\" title\u003d\"Toggle fullscreen\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--zoom\" title\u003d\"Zoom in/out\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__icn\"\u003e\n       \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__prel